Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:44.92,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H9F66E6&\pos(354,301)}這裏由{\fs30}我來{\fs20\c&H13AFF9&}上{\c&HD7C346&\fs30}就夠了
